<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَعَلِيٌّ}</span> ... رَفِيعُ الشَّانِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَكِيمٌ}</span> ... مُحْكَمٌ، وَذُو حِكْمَةٍ بَالِغَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَفَنَضْرِبُ عَنكُمُ الذِّكْرَ صَفْحًا}</span> ... أَفَنُعْرِضُ عَنْكُمْ، وَنَتْرُكُ تَذْكِيرَكُمْ بِالقُرْآنِ؟!<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَن كُنتُمْ}</span> ... بِسَبَبِ أَنْ كُنْتُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَكَمْ أَرْسَلْنَا}</span> ... كَثِيرًا مِنَ الأَنْبِيَاءِ أَرْسَلْنَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بَطْشًا}</span> ... قُوَّةً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَضَى مَثَلُ الْأَوَّلِينَ}</span> ... سَبَقَ فيِ القُرْآنِ أَحَادِيثُ إِهْلَاكِهِمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَهْدًا}</span> ... فِرَاشًا مُمَهَّدًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُبُلًا}</span> ... طُرُقًا لِمَعَاشِكُمْ تَسْلُكُونَهَا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
